<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
    integrity="sha384-EVSTQN3/azprG1Anm3QDgpJLIm9Nao0Yz1ztcQTwFspd3yD65VohhpuuCOmLASjC" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
    integrity="sha384-MrcW6ZMFYlzcLA8Nl+NtUVF0sA7MsXsP1UyJoMp4YLEuNSfAP+JcXn/tWtIaxVXM"
    crossorigin="anonymous">
    </script>

    <!-------------------- jQuery, Axios CDN IMPORT ---------------------->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/axios/dist/axios.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Gowun+Dodum&family=Ubuntu&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    
    <link href="/admin/css/workshops-request.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <script src="/admin/js/workshops-request.js" defer></script>
    
    <title>Document</title>
</head>
<style>

</style>
<body>
    <!--헤더 nav-bar-->
    <%- include('header.ejs') %>

    <div class="wrapper">
        <!--sidebar 구역입니다.-->
        <div class="sidebar">
            <div class="ul-title">워크숍 관리</div>
            <ul class="ul-category">
                <li class="target-li active-li" onclick="location.href='workshops-request'">- 검토 대기중인 워크숍</li>
                <li class="target-li link-li" onclick="location.href='workshops-approval'">- 현재 진행중인 워크숍</li>
                <li class="target-li link-li" onclick="location.href='workshops-finished'">- 종료된 워크숍</li>  
            </ul>
            <div class="ul-title">유저 및 업체 관리</div>
            <ul class="ul-category">
                <li class="target-li link-li" onclick="location.href='black-register'">- 블랙리스트 등록하기</li>
                <li class="target-li link-li" onclick="location.href='black-list'">- 블랙리스트 목록</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="ul-title">관리자 계정 관리</div>
            <ul class="ul-category">
                <li class="target-li link-li" onclick="location.href='admin-manage'">- 관리자 계정 등록 및 삭제</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <!--main-content 구역입니다.-->
        <div class="main-content">
            <div class="workshop-search">현재 검토중인 워크숍 목록입니다.
                <div class="search-wrap">
                      <select class="form-select">
                          <option value="1">강사 이메일</option>
                          <option value="2">워크숍 타이틀</option>
                        </select>
                    <input class="search-box" type="text" placeholder="검색어 입력">
                    <button class="search-button">검색</button>
                  </div>
            </div>
            <!-- 워크숍 목록입니다.-->
            <div class="card-wrapper" >
                <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-4 g-4" id="workshop-list">
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 워크숍 상세 (모달) -->
            <div id="modal-btn">123</div>

            <div class="modal" id="modal" tabindex="-1">
                  <div class="modal-content">
                    <div class="modal-header">
                      <h5 class="modal-title">워크숍 상세내용</h5>
                      <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="modal-body">
                        <div class="modal-image">
                            <img src="/images/admin-image/workshop-example.jpg"></img>
                        </div>
                        <div class="info">
                            <div class="info-category">온라인</div>
                            <div class="info-title">제목입니다</div>
                            <div class="info-desc">강의에 대한 설명입니다.</div>
                            <div class="info-ul">인원 :
                                <span class="info-li" style="font-weight:bold;">최소 10명 ~ 최대 100명</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="info-ul">시간 :
                                <span class="info-li" >120분</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="info-ul">장르 :
                                <span class="info-li">문화예술</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="info-ul">목적 :
                                <span class="info-li">동기부여, 팀워크</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="info-ul">강사 이름 :
                                <span class="info-li">홍길동</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="info-ul">강사 이메일 :
                                <span class="info-li">user1@test.com</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="info-price">30,000원<span>최저가</span></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="modal-footer">
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" id="create">승인하기</button>
                      <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal" id="close-btn">반려하기</button>
                    </div>
                  </div>
              </div>
        </div>   
    </div>

</body>
</html>